    "Both models are capable of continuously acquiring rewards in complex and variable environments until convergence.",
    "Notably, the final test rewards of GDMs are significantly higher than those for DRL-PPO under identical parameter settings, allowing the MLLM service provider to consistently secure greater utilities.",
